Title: 2. Stakeholders
Write-Up Text: In these social media posts people are commenting on the Australian budget presentation and offering their opinions on the proposals. The posts highlight various key areas including the allocation of funds for green hydrogen government taxes and the subsidies for aged care services. The quotes from respected economists and politicians who provide feedback on the budget proposal are shared and analyzed. The hashtags #auspol and #budgetinreply are used to denote the Australian political context where politicians and their supporters actively discuss the budget proposal.
